household dataset to be used as an example

sample_dataset.Rd

This dataset comes from the Host Community Multi Sector Needs Assessment conducted in 2018 by IMPACT/REACH on behalf of the ISCG and funded by ECHO. This is a sample of the data collected in both Ukhia and Teknaf. For privacy purpose, the GPS coordinates are faked but are still located in the designated areas.

sample_dataset
